Package: pyfort-py23
Version: 8.4
Revision: 1
Description: Python-Fortran connection tool (python23 version)
DescDetail: <<
Pyfort is a tool for creating extensions to the Python language with
Fortran routines. It supports F77-interfaced routines now, 
with plans for supporting more of F90 later.
Install pyfort23 SplitOff to make symlink pyfort --> pyfort2.3
<<
Source: mirror:sourceforge:pyfortran/Pyfort-%v.tar.gz    
Source-MD5: 1e05f37e0169bd14e43e1923efe77da3
Patch: %n.patch
Replaces: pyfort
Depends: python23, numeric-py23, g77
SourceDirectory: Pyfort-%v
CompileScript: %p/bin/python2.3 setup.py build
InstallScript: <<
 %p/bin/python2.3 setup.py install --prefix=%i
 mkdir -p %i/share/doc/%n
 cp -R test testc demo %i/share/doc/%n
 mv %i/bin/pyfort %i/bin/pyfort2.3
 ln -s %p/bin/pyfort2.3 %i/bin/pyfort
<<
DescPort: patch to make g77 default compiler.
